title: War of the Roses: He's Married and She Doesn't Care
description: Jamie is causing a lot of drama on this week's War of the Roses.  She's seeing a married man and she doesn't care what anyone thinks about it.  She's doing Roses to make sure that he's leaving his wife for her like he says but when we get him on the phone, let's just say... plot twist!
